2
00:00:41,553 --> 00:00:43,367
Saya lebih takut...

3
00:00:43,703 --> 00:00:45,753
kehilangan awak
daripada kehilangan peluang...

4
00:00:46,343 --> 00:00:49,250
dalam industri ini,
hanya kerana skandal.

5
00:00:49,772 --> 00:00:51,124
Jadi...

6
00:00:53,294 --> 00:00:55,164
mari mulakan semula.

7
00:01:00,509 --> 00:01:02,983
Awak masih mahu melepaskan saya?

8
00:01:07,143 --> 00:01:08,582
Jika awak lepaskan sekarang,

9
00:01:10,549 --> 00:01:11,896
kita takkan...

10
