berjumpa satu sama lain lagi.

11
00:01:36,366 --> 00:01:37,790
Cik Oh Jin Sim.

12
00:01:47,383 --> 00:01:48,725
Saya cintakan awak.

13
00:02:22,571 --> 00:02:24,403
(Episod 15)

14
